<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Plată Reușită — AgentulMeu</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{--bg:#fff;--bg-2:#f8f9fa;--text:#111;--text-2:#555;--text-3:#888;--accent:#C9A227;--green:#16a34a;--border:rgba(0,0,0,0.06);--shadow-lg:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);--radius-xl:28px}
@keyframes float{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateY(-6px)}}
@keyframes fadeInUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes scaleIn{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(0.5)}to{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}}
@keyframes checkDraw{to{stroke-dashoffset:0}}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;line-height:1.6}
.fade-in{animation:fadeInUp .5s ease-out both}

nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.nav-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none}
.nav-logo-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green),#15803d);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:800;font-size:1rem;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(22,163,74,0.3)}
.nav-logo-text{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
.nav-logo-text span{color:var(--accent)}
.nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px}
.nav-links a{color:var(--text-2);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:500;transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
.btn-nav{padding:8px 18px;border-radius:10px;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s}
.btn-nav-primary{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}
.btn-nav-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-1px)}

main{flex:1;padding:88px 24px 60px;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;text-align:center}

.success-card{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:48px 40px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);animation:fadeInUp .5s ease-out both}

.check-circle{width:80px;height:80px;margin:0 auto 24px;animation:scaleIn .5s ease-out .2s both}
.check-circle svg{width:100%;height:100%}
.check-circle .circle{fill:none;stroke:var(--green);stroke-width:3;stroke-dasharray:166;stroke-dashoffset:166;animation:checkDraw .6s ease-out .4s forwards}
.check-circle .check{fill:none;stroke:var(--green);stroke-width:4;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-dasharray:48;stroke-dashoffset:48;animation:checkDraw .3s ease-out .8s forwards}

h1{font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--green)}
.subtitle{color:var(--text-2);font-size:0.92rem;margin-bottom:32px}

.next-steps{text-align:left;background:var(--bg-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;margin-bottom:28px}
.next-steps h3{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px}
.next-steps ol{padding-left:20px;color:var(--text-2);font-size:0.88rem}
.next-steps li{margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.5}
.next-steps li strong{color:var(--text)}

.btn-next{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:14px;border:none;font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s ease;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;background:var(--accent);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(249,115,22,0.25);text-decoration:none}
.btn-next:hover{background:#ea580c;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(249,115,22,0.35)}

footer{text-align:center;padding:24px;color:var(--text-3);font-size:0.75rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}

@media(max-width:600px){
  .nav-links{display:none}
  .success-card{padding:32px 24px}
}
</style>
  
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/uploads/logoagentulmeu/favicon.png">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/assets/uploads/logoagentulmeu/favicon.ico">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/premium-design.css">
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
      
      <div class="nav-logo-text">Agentul<span>Meu</span></div>
    </a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/">Acasă</a>
      <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-nav btn-nav-primary">Mergi la Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<main>
  <div class="success-card">
    <div class="check-circle">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 52 52">
        <circle class="circle" cx="26" cy="26" r="25"/>
        <path class="check" d="M14.1 27.2l7.1 7.2 16.7-16.8"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
    <h1>Plată reușită! 🎉</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Mulțumim! Contul tău a fost activat cu succes.</p>
    
    <div class="next-steps">
      <h3>📋 Următorii pași:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Completează wizard-ul</strong> — Definește business-ul tău în 8 pași simpli</li>
        <li><strong>Generează fișierele MD</strong> — AI-ul creează automat cele 9 module</li>
        <li><strong>Instalează Hermes</strong> — O singură comandă pe VPS-ul tău</li>
        <li><strong>Conectează canalele</strong> — Telegram, WhatsApp sau Web Chat</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-next">🚀 Mergi la Dashboard</a>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>© 2026 AgentulMeu.online · Made in România 🇷🇴</footer>
</body>
</html>
